aboutUsTitle: We are students from Princess Noura University, from the Department of History and Archeology, Faculty of Humanities and Social Sciences. Presenting our project is an application that serves and supports the 2030 vision for preserving antiquities and history in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, specifically Souq Okaz, which is located in the city of Taif. It is an application that serves tourists and market visitors
okazTitle: Souq Okaz is the most important and famous market for the Arabs. It is located in the northeast of the city of Taif. It carries historical importance as the Arabs used to gather there to buy and sell, and listen to poets and preachers. History has recorded that Souq Okaz played a prominent literary role in pre-Islamic times, and the market continued until the year 129 AH.
